Title: Email Intro
Subject Line: Introduction to Matt at Triple R
Content:
I wanted to touch base and see if you'd be open to a brief introduction to Matt at Triple R Marketing.

The reason I thought of you is they've really found the key to helping communities have their own online store, with your oversight built in, which saves time, maintains brand control, and removes a lot of the busywork that usually comes with it.

If you're open to it, I'm happy to make the intro.
